Jool is a gas giant planet with Laythe and two other small unnamed planets orbiting it.

[note]As is logical, landing on a gas giant is impossible, but this doesn't prevent us from gathering resources from this giant.[/note]

Jool's atmosphere consists of helium-3 (25%), liquid hydrogen (25%), chlorine (20%), and neon (12%).\nTo collect all these gases, we will need a harvester.
